Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[芙蓉 枫 篇 前篇]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在旅行的归途中遇到了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和土见夫妻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠男主人一个养大女儿会很不容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说还要一起照顾土见家的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令嫒入院已经有两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来母亲的事情对她的打击很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就像是拒绝活下去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行 只要能给她生存的动力 生存的目的 相信一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫 听的到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的事情 你觉得很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些话没对小枫你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 阿姨她会死是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人看家觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就非要她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就在回来的路上遇到了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 枫 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起这里就是禀的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大的行李我已经帮你搬进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等静下心了和枫一起下楼来吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安 小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的作业你做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 禀 还习惯在这个家里的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫怎么样 有和禀好好相处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心弄掉了 帮我捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妈妈死了 你却活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人死了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是写给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 死的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等枫的病好了 下次要一起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病？ 我的病？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 枫又发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是复发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得出去旅行实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 她说马上就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说了谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我把妈妈...害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 禀 请用早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说枫 之前我也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上吃吃面包什么的就...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想吃面包的话 明天就吃西式的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 培根烤蛋和洋葱汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都做这么丰盛很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾禀的起居是我的生存乐趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的便当是鳕鱼西京烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次伯父出差的时间会很长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是去海外了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的 说是会花上3-4个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系嘛 让年轻男女独处这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明他十分信赖禀你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门的时候还对我说什么「父母公认要加油哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该多为女儿的将来考虑一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单是因为和我同居就已经没什么男人缘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他应该已经很为我着想了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了 土见禀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是小枫亲卫队一定一定小枫略称KKK的Magnum界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你真的是高中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把身心都献给禀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我是想说想献给他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 纠正的太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天亲卫队也来了两三人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每天早上都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要为奉陪他们的我想想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫 扑入我的怀中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿叶同学 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 这些下次测验会出的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知会出还做错的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是名副其实的笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是名副其实的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我也一样 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 这可不是可以挺起胸膛夸耀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人 我记了笔记 等一会我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琳 我也拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人 请用便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒...蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起变化更注重量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...这全部恐怕吃不完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会吃的 我今天刚好想吃炒蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃 奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子充满着爱的手制料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算弄破胃也要吃干净才算男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀对女孩还不够温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 禀 胃药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀已经温柔到不能再温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在去给你倒水 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用和他一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想学一下新的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小禀真是个幸运儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只能为他做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧的好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫烫烫 水水水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不能加水的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事我会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀不去上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我已经请假休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以 因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀请假不去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就回房静养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经没事了 之后就由我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello 小禀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带炸面包和作业来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想两位可能会为了晚饭发愁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不会添麻烦的话 可以让我们来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 但这是我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 看来很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天在学校见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 小禀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧 多少吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天实在对不起了 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 生病的时候好歹也考虑休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我帮上你的忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 有没有给禀添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是不在比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是地震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是那么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给你添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没有枫在就什么都做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也能让我照顾你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就答应我一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微放松一些轻松一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是枫再累倒了 又要像今天这样引起大骚动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀用他的温柔拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止一直 相信以后也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太温柔了所以易受他人仰慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也无法做到身边只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看到禀的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能听到禀说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能精神起来 也觉得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能陪在禀的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一直让我陪在你身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为照顾禀的起居是我的生活乐趣
